data.description: Unlock the door to your new home in The Farm at Morgan Lakes, a gated haven in Pooler. This 4 bed, 2.5 bath home with a loft is the perfect blend of style & functionality. Enjoy open-concept living, including a gourmet kitchen with white cabinets, oversized island, walk-in pantry, double ovens, & separate cooktop. A built-in drop-zone at the garage entry adds convenience. The versatile formal space can serve as a dining room or office. The spacious owner’s retreat features a supersized tiled shower and generous walk-in closet. The secondary bedrooms have ample closet storage. Relax on the covered front & back porches. White vinyl privacy fence. Fully irrigated yard. Amenities include a 2-story clubhouse, resort-style pools, kids splash park, fitness center, playground, and 65-acre lake with a boat dock. Reach Pooler’s shopping, restaurants, I-95, I-16, or the airport in mere minutes!
